cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.HC 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with facial action unit detection and face alignment, which are both tasks related to computer vision. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes an end-to-end deep learning framework for joint AU detection and face alignment. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper uses adaptive attention learning module to refine the attention map of each AU adaptively. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with facial expression analysis, which is a common task in multimedia applications. 
5. cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) is also possible as the paper deals with facial expression analysis, which is an important aspect of human-computer interaction.
